{"id":152249,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/研究人员研制出基于石墨烯的光调制器/","date":"2011-05-14T13:30:27Z","modified":"2011-05-14T13:30:27Z","title":"研究人员研制出基于石墨烯的光调制器","content":"<p>加州大学伯克利分校的研究人员研发出(中文)基于石墨烯的光调制器，能使数字通信速度提高10倍。 伯克利工程学教授Xiang Zhang表示，石墨烯使调制器更紧凑，有潜力使速度比目前技术所允许的快上十倍。新技术将会大幅强化超快光通讯与运算的能力。他们的研究发表在上周的《自然》期刊上。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14d0abf1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E7%A0%94%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%A8%E7%83%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E8%B0%83%E5%88%B6%E5%99%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F1136238%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E7%A0%94%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%A8%E7%83%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E8%B0%83%E5%88%B6%E5%99%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F1136238%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092210404/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14d0abf1/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092210404/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14d0abf1/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=gZriEiVvTbA:SGqu5-3gbuk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=gZriEiVvTbA:SGqu5-3gbuk:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" acti